description:
eBuds is a fair and transparent NFT project, where everyone can join, contribute and take advantage of the benefits.

eBuds team members are not taking any fees, they are investing their time and money to build a strong community, with a long term vision.

eBuds is built on MultiversX and is a decentralized autonomous organization that is governed by the eBuds Community. Itâ€™s one of the first DAOs powered by @SUPERCIETY. The eBudsDAO manages the $EBUD Token, a cryptocurrency that is used to power the eBuds ecosystem.
